        <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-medium text-ink mb-2">How to set a timer online?</h3>
        <p class="text-body text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
          To set a timer online, visit onlinetimer.in and tap the countdown display to open the duration picker. Enter your desired hours, minutes, and seconds — for example, you can quickly set an <strong>online timer 10 minutes</strong>, <strong>online timer 5 minutes</strong>, or <strong>online timer 30 minutes</strong>. Then press the Start button to begin counting down. The circular progress ring will visually show how much time remains. You can pause, reset, or share your timer at any point.
        </p>
