      <div class="border-b border-hairline pb-4">
        <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-medium text-ink mb-2">What is an online timer?</h3>
        <p class="text-body text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
          An <strong>online timer</strong> is a web-based tool that runs directly in your browser to measure and manage time. Unlike physical timers or traditional stopwatches, an <strong>online timer</strong> requires no downloads, installations, or plugins. It works on any device with a modern browser — desktop, laptop, tablet, or smartphone. Online timers come in many forms including countdown timers, stopwatches, pomodoro timers, and world clocks, making them versatile tools for work, study, fitness, and daily life.
        </p>
      </div>

